Job Description:
● To be a mixologist/Barista, providing technical supports (R&D, training, demonstrating.. ect) for all clients of LongBeach, especially key accounts;
● Research & innovate drink concepts and update drinking trend for customer's LTO as well as internal communication;
● Manage, operate & preserve LongBeach studio;
● Following up and executing all LongBeach brand’s activations and sponsorship/events according to plan (measurement, analysis, and propose adjusting plan);
● Setup and operating and report of LongBeach branding activities monthly;
● Support sales team to get more customers;
● To assist, operate & participating in events in request as Road Show and Exhibitions (Such as Food and Hotel Vietnam, Cafe Show, VIETFOOD or related exhibition);
● Take responsible work as assigned and Report to supervisors upon request.

Location: Ho Chi Minh City and Nationwide (Vietnam)
Reports to: Sales Director (in Thailand) / BI Manager; Sales Manager (Vietnam)
Conditions of Service: Full-time

Job Requirements:
- Tốt nghiệp Đại học trở lên các ngành: Quản trị kinh doanh, kinh tế, thương mại,...
- Có trên 2 năm kinh nghiệm ở vị trí tương đương chuyên về lĩnh vực Gạch, ngói, thiết bị nhà tắm, nhà bếp, công cụ dụng cụ, điện sơn…;
- Có khả năng quản lý, đào tạo nhân sự tốt;
- Giao tiếp tốt, yêu thích công việc kinh doanh, không ngại đi công tác;
- Trung thực, năng động, tinh thần tự giác cao, gắn bó lâu dài;
- Kỹ năng làm việc độc lập, làm việc nhóm.

• Graduated from university, major in Civil & Structural Engineering, and related fields;
• Having at least 3 years of working experience in structural engineering design in a foreign corporation;
• Have experience in project management over 4 years;
• Licensed as a professional engineer
• Having deep understanding of software design, structural analysis, software priority such as: ETABS, SAFE, RAPT, PLAXIS, SAP 2000, CAD, REVIT, and office software;
• Understand international construction law and design standards;
• Having the ability to read and understand technical documents, having good English communication is an advantage;
• Having sense of discipline, modern working style; having the ability to work under pressure, willing to work overtime

Benefit:
• Attractive salary with bonus
• 15 days Annual leave per year
• 100% salary for probation period
• Premium healthcare insurance (PTI – included legal spouse and children), Accident insurance 24/24, SOS worldwide insurance
• Fixed 13th month salary, API – Annual Performance Incentive (Bonus)
• Regular appropriate on-job and oversea training courses

Job Description:
